WebCenter MCI XSLT Tool

Currently, exports of Task Types, Attribute Categories and entire Project Templates are supported. Note that multiple Task Types, Attribute Categories and Project Templates exported to one XML file are supported.

If anything is missing or not working as expected, please contact the initiative team

Projects

JavaScript Rule Actions

JavaScript Rule Action Name: Set Project Status to "Obsolescence Process"

Name Set Project Status to "Obsolescence Process"
Description
Script var actualProject= API.getProject();
actualProject.setStatusByName('Obsolescence Process');

JavaScript Rule Action Name: Cancelation Actions

Name Cancelation Actions
Description
Script var actualProject = API.getProject();
var state = actualProject.getAttribute('GEN_ProjectState');
state.setValue(String(1));
actualProject.setStatusByName(String('Canceled'));

    Rules Setup

    Rule Action: Cancelation
    Name Cancelation
    Description
    Order 1
    Enabled 1
    JSON {"triggers":[{"attributeName":"Gen_CancelationReason","type":"ProjectAttribute"}],"actions":[{"type":"StartTask","taskTypeName":"Cancel Project"},{"javaScriptName":"Cancelation Actions","type":"JavaScriptAction"}]}
    Rule Action: Startup Obsolescence
    Name Startup Obsolescence
    Description
    Order 2
    Enabled 1
    JSON {"triggers":[{"attributeName":"GEN_DateObsolescence","subtype":"ProjectAttribute","offset":0,"type":"DateTimeReached"}],"actions":[{"javaScriptName":"Set Project Status to \"Obsolescence Process\"","type":"JavaScriptAction"},{"type":"StartTask","taskTypeName":"Obsolescence Workflow"}]}

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName Default

    Button Details ProjectCreation view

    set Obsolescence Date button
    func JavaScript
    label set Obsolescence Date
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript var d = new Date();
    d.setFullYear(d.getFullYear() + 3);
    att["GEN_DateObsolescence"] = d;
    execOnLoad true
    viewName ProjectCreation
    Set Date button
    func JavaScript
    label Set Date
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript if (att["GEN_DateSubmitted"] === "") {
    var d = new Date();
    att["GEN_DateSubmitted"] = d;
    }
    execOnLoad true
    viewName ProjectCreation
    Set Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label Set Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName ProjectCreation

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName TaskExecution

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true

    Button Details TaskExecution view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }

    Workflow Node Rename Project (executeJS_9)

    Parameters:

    Node Parameter Name Node Parameter Value
    executeJS.javaScript /*
    * Instantiate the Project Object
    */
    var project = API.getProject();
    /*
    * Retrieve the actual project name
    */
    var actualProjectName = project.getName();
    /*
    * Instantiate a Date Object
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Build a UTC human readable date
    */
    var utc = d.getUTCFullYear() + ":" + d.getUTCMonth() + ":" + d.getUTCDate() + "_" + d.getUTCHours() + ":" + d.getUTCMinutes() + ":" + d.getUTCSeconds() + ":" + d.getUTCMilliseconds();
    /*
    * Build the new Project Name
    */
    var newProjectName = actualProjectName + "_Canceled_" + utc;
    /*
    * Set the project Name
    */
    project.setName(newProjectName);

    Transitions:

    Transition name Transition to

    		 00001_0000000003_3 (Completed)

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true

    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName Default

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName Default

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName TaskExecution

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName Default

    Button Details TaskExecution view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }

    Button Details Default view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }

    Button Details TaskExecution view

    save Comments History button
    func JavaScript
    label save Comments History
    style hidden
    changeAtts
    javaScript /*
    * Return a well formated string for a date rendering
    * @param {integer} number
    * @returns {String}
    */
    function setCorrectNumberFormat(number) {
    var result = '';
    if (String(number).length === 1) {
    result = '0' + String(number);
    } else {
    result = String(number);
    }
    return result;
    }

    /*
    * Execute the script if the GEN_Comments attribute is not empty
    */
    if (/.*\S.*/.test(att['GEN_Comments'])) {
    /*
    * Create the current user name string
    */
    var userName = gCurrentUser['firstName'] + ' ' + gCurrentUser['lastName'];
    /*
    * instanciate a new date object (by default current date)
    */
    var d = new Date();
    /*
    * Collect the actual content of the Comments history
    */
    var oldComments = att['GEN_CommentsHistory'];
    /*
    * Collect the content of the new Comment
    */
    var newComment = att['GEN_Comments'];
    /*
    * Create the UTC date String
    */
    var utcDate = 'UTC ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCDate()) + '-' + d.getUTCFullYear() + ' at ' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCHours()) + ':' + setCorrectNumberFormat(d.getUTCMinutes());
    /*
    * Create the new string to store in the Comments history
    */
    var newComments = "â¢ " + userName + " wrote on " + utcDate + " â¢ \r\n" + newComment + '\r\n\r\n' + oldComments;
    /*
    * Set the value of Comments History Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_CommentsHistory'] = newComments;
    /*
    * Reset the Comment Attribute
    */
    att['GEN_Comments'] = "";
    }
    execOnSave true
    viewName TaskExecution
